{"TopicId":96074,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Need Help Turning Planet Color Map Into Normal Map (Kopernicus)","CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-09T02:39:51Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-09T02:39:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI released my Odysseus planet pack about a week ago, and one of the biggest issues is that whatever the moons\u0027 template was set to, that would become their \u0022shape\u0022 in map view and from high orbit. I found that this was caused by improper normal maps, which I had exported straight from Space Engine. I don\u0027t know why these don\u0027t work, but they don\u0027t. So, if anyone knows how I can turn color maps into normals maps I would really like to know how! Thanks!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere are the color maps for the celestial bodies that don\u0027t work:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/w4O23fM.png\u0022 alt=\u0022w4O23fM.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/XYe3v3y.png\u0022 alt=\u0022XYe3v3y.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/GbTosR6.png\u0022 alt=\u0022GbTosR6.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/O24aFgN.png\u0022 alt=\u0022O24aFgN.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tygoo7","CreatedById":57345,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-09T03:08:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECan you post the normal maps by any chance? I\u0027ll attempt to see if I can help you fix this. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-09T21:36:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ESure thing! Here they are and in the same order as the color maps above:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/csyjYUN.png\u0022 alt=\u0022csyjYUN.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/PC2XgBy.png\u0022 alt=\u0022PC2XgBy.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/f69ih32.png\u0022 alt=\u0022f69ih32.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/O9wP5ry.png\u0022 alt=\u0022O9wP5ry.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tygoo7","CreatedById":57345,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-10T00:42:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHere try this one to see if it works. It\u0027s only the first one for now.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/wFsNeCi.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022wFsNeCi.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Thomas988","CreatedById":92699,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-10T01:23:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENope, doesn\u0027t work. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E As a reference, here is the normal map for Verviedi, a moon from _Augustus_\u0027s Stella Expansion pack. This does indeed work.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/WrvYJvg.png\u0022 alt=\u0022WrvYJvg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Clonos","CreatedById":169038,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-07T09:41:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think you have to set opacity to 50% to make it work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NickRoss120","CreatedById":174028,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-07T16:29:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d really hate to necro-post, but \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/169038-genesisplayz/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022169038\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/169038-genesisplayz/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@GenesisPlayz\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0It has to be a DTX5_nm DDS\u00A0compression, not just a decreased opacity of a normal map, that won\u0027t work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Clonos","CreatedById":169038,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-07T19:48:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/174028-nickross120/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022174028\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/174028-nickross120/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@NickRoss120\u003C/a\u003EHuh. It works for me, and i saved it as DXT3 Expliet Alpha or something, and it works like a charm.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NickRoss120","CreatedById":174028,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-07T19:51:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell I meant to say that it was supposed to be a DTX5nm because it makes it face the sun and not to the side, but I\u0027ll try the DTX3ea and see if that works.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeltaDizzy","CreatedById":150755,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-08T05:32:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe program I\u0027m using doesn\u0027t have DXT5_nm as an option.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vorg","CreatedById":74652,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-08-09T02:48:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGimp has a plugin for normals and such, but finding the right setting is....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}